# Data Contracts

Use this directory for project-specific data contracts once your starter grows real schemas or compatibility surfaces.

Recommended structure:
- `contracts/schemas/`: versioned JSON Schema, OpenAPI fragments, protobuf, or other schema sources
- `tests/fixtures/data_contracts/`: sample payloads and compatibility fixtures

Starter rule:
- keep at least one machine-readable schema or fixture per contract once `data_contract` changes become part of the project
